rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Magomago's Grampypon
is always busy, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0002
rows.name:
In other places, lots of people
bring goods, but it's different
here, so it's tough, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0003
rows.name:
You can't bring goods unless you
get permission from the big shots,
mo. Anything? Anything, mo?

rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Hurry up and be night, mo!
Grampypon's work, be over, mo!
